summary: I'm thankful for @danielhowell and @amazingphil who inspired me to get my life together, who always make my day better, and have...
body:
I’m thankful for @danielhowell and @amazingphil who inspired me to get my life together, who always make my day better, and have helped me with mental health, embracing my softer side, introduced me to things I now love… I could go on and on but Imma leave it there lol;

I’m thankful for @marigoldan for being my internet sister and her constant posting which makes me smile just about every day;

I’m thankful for @thatsthat24 for his videos which both entertain me and help me learn new things about myself;

Grateful for my friends @honeyjarhowell @deutschedori @trashtrashtrash776 who I don’t speak to often but am still grateful for!

And of course I’m grateful for @pxheart (highly recommend her posters btw) @incaseyouart @edorazzi @inkjackets @harrywavycurly @tokyo-fashion @potoobrigham ((i know i’m forgetting people and I’m s o r r y)) for just brightening up my day in general!

Happy Thanksgiving to all those who celebrate it!! And thanks to @optimistphan for hosting this meetup!

summary: I don’t want to hear Dan and Phil EVER complain about their so called “cold” England weather EVER AGAIN.  Quebec, today, while...
body:
I don’t want to hear Dan and Phil EVER complain about their so called “cold” England weather EVER AGAIN. 

Quebec, today, while the sun is gleaming on the snow (we are in NOVEMBER), it’s -16 degree celsius (feels like -23 degree celsius). I can’t. I just… It’s November, it’s too early for me to bring a blanket to class…
